text: Keshia Knight Pulliam (born April 9, 1979) is an American actress. She is best known for her television performances. She played Rudy Huxtable in the NBC situation comedy The Cosby Show (1984-1992). Before that, she acted on Sesame Street. Knight Pulliam was born in Newark, New Jersey. ==References== Category:Actors from New Jersey Category:American television actors Category:1979 births Category:Living people
